title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Slann Starmaster
description:
Ancient beings created to serve the Old Ones, the Starmasters are among the greatest wizards in all the realms. Follow this step-by-step guide to get your Slann Starmaster painted to a Battle Ready standard in no time at all.         
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.

title: How to Paint: Commander Dante #Shorts
description: Dante is master of the Blood Angels and the bringer of Sanguinius' light. Follow this step-by-step guide to learn how to paint this gold-clad legend in no time. We'll also show you some simple additional steps to really take this angelic paint job to the next level.  #Shorts

title: Discover Citadel Colour: The App
description: The Citadel Colour app is your essential painting companion. With features such as: Paint by Colour, Paint by Model and Inventory & Wishlist you'll be painting miniatures you can be proud of regardless of your skill level! https://bit.ly/3B1RABp
